{"tid":620740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戴耀廷:2019區議會更多民主派參選,2020立法會投票率上升至六成!","createTime":"2018-04-07T18:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T03:05:06.000Z","uid":49388,"like":9,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"825034e47c7bf5e46a0b9b91c06433372e9b1c2b","tid":620740,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T18:15:47.000Z","msg":"香港大學法律系副教授戴耀廷早前在台灣出席論壇時，提到若中國專政結束，香港可考慮獨立成國或與中國其他族群組成聯邦，引起港府、中聯辦等輪流發炮。民陣和民主派議員周六傍晚在立法會示威區舉行「撐言論自由  撐學術自由  撐戴耀廷」集會。戴耀廷表示，過去一星期沒想過會受到文革式批鬥情況下，心情很沉重，但見到大家都在這裏，心裏暖意很大。<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷並談到2019年區議會選舉，民主派將有大約300人參選，選舉合共有452個議席，他期望會有更多香港人出來參選，令每個議席都有民主人士出選。至於2020年立法會選舉，他期望將投票率推上六成，認為每一票都是投資，代表香港民主未來，希望可以用民主反專制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/11272/%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-11272/%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%97%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A9%E5%BC%8F%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E5%BE%88%E6%B2%89%E9%87%8D-%E7%9B%BC%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F11272%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258D%25A8-%25E8%25A8%2580%25E8%25AB%2596%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1-11272%2F%25E6%2588%25B4%25E8%2580%2580%25E5%25BB%25B7%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2596%2587%25E9%259D%25A9%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2589%25B9%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25BF%2583%25E6%2583%2585%25E5%25BE%2588%25E6%25B2%2589%25E9%2587%258D-%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8&d=P08BAzofc8OAu%2FS17Cd%2BQsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=67d996ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/11272/%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7-%E6%B8%AF%E7%8D%A8-%E8%A8%80%E8%AB%96%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1-11272/%E6%88%B4%E8%80%80%E5%BB%B7%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%97%E6%96%87%E9%9D%A9%E5%BC%8F%E6%89%B9%E9%AC%A5%E5%BF%83%E6%83%85%E5%BE%88%E6%B2%89%E9%87%8D-%E7%9B%BC%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E4%BE%86%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8</a>"},{"pid":"d1b3747160fb7dbbed67e074a23e0fdac2094cdf","tid":620740,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T23:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a120f8424c6ef9c98add6f4af0b535a06ab7f36","tid":620740,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T23:52:44.000Z","msg":"唔唔  閱"},{"pid":"d7bf3dc30e135f9184ef4466c5fd73b7fbe0afba","tid":620740,"uid":12449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T00:02:02.000Z","msg":"泛民講大話 <br />\n<br />\n自己打壓完就攞陳浩天梁天琦嘅論述<br />\n<br />\n民主黨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/thedphk/posts/10153903886789889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthedphk%2Fposts%2F10153903886789889&d=P08BAzofc8OAu%2FS17Cd%2BQsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cd03ecf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/thedphk/posts/10153903886789889</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨就旺角衝突發表聲明如下：<br />\n<br />\n1.民主黨不容忍和譴責任何暴力和縱火行為，對於有記者採訪期間遇襲受傷，深表憤怒，並譴責襲擊前線警員的暴力行為，對受傷人士致以慰問。<br />\n<br />\n2. 襲擊警員事件與向天開槍示警事件均需全面調查，公開結果，追究違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n3. 要求政府全面檢討社會嚴重矛盾的深層原因, 包括民憤不斷累積爆發、港府為何失去管治威信及今次導火線的小販政策。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公民黨<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/posts/10153384344558457\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcivicpartyhk%2Fposts%2F10153384344558457&d=P08BAzofc8OAu%2FS17Cd%2BQsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=4650e5c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/civicpartyhk/posts/10153384344558457</a><br />\n<br />\n公民黨聲明<br />\n2016年2月9日發出<br />\n<br />\n1.新春假期街頭小販營生，要管理而非趕絕，但政府一直無適當策略。今次由旺角一宗民生事件而起，因處理欠佳，發酵為騷亂，原是可以避免的。<br />\n<br />\n2.有示威者縱火、掟磚、襲擊警員和記者，多人受傷，財物損毀。公民黨譴責暴力行為。同時，一名警員在鬧市鳴槍示警，易傷無辜，行為是否恰當，必須深入調查，向公眾交代。<br />\n<br />\n3. 記者正常採訪受阻、受襲，工作器材被惡性損壞，嚴重破壞新聞自由，公民黨絕對不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n4. 暴力無助解決問題，而且會令社會將焦點轉而至騷亂，而非小販政策問題本身。因此我們譴責使用暴力者，認為他們必須承擔使用暴力的法律後果。"},{"pid":"10456de6d66abf803acae8bc2e00a45a31ae88b0","tid":620740,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"泛民屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n屌大學生都唔撚上得台講<br />\n<br />\n之前又話比兩間su 出黎<br />\n<br />\n到你拖左馬又話只準學聯發聲<br />\n(學聯？ 邊撚度聯呀？睇過？）<br />\n<br />\n咁少事都專制到咁<br />\n<br />\n睇撚死你2019 又要未選先告急<br />\n<br />\n早兩個月就屌票又話上次你班焦土撚點點點<br />\n<br />\n張張票都刻撚左泛民個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246958f3e6e14a82d2e954f2915c62ebdc130b47","tid":620740,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T01:38:07.000Z","msg":"原來保皇狗打手行緊巴路線係<br />\n支持戴同時又暗助保皇狗<br />\n睇來全部夾埋收緊香港言論自由"},{"pid":"0e2071f2650c978048b1c31fde3c1753a0327bd2","tid":620740,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T01:47:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e99b72ce33282d7f8be7a8e2e189cfcf2c4d9c17","tid":620740,"uid":72301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T02:02:08.000Z","msg":"繼續𠝹票 保皇fatfat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd403b1f1178a7dafc9a96d6d56d33cad277f8e","tid":620740,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10456de6d66abf803acae8bc2e00a45a31ae88b0","tid":620740,"uid":51701,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"泛民屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n屌大學生都唔撚上得台講<br />\n<br />\n之前又話比兩間su 出黎<br />\n<br />\n到你拖左馬又話只準學聯發聲<br />\n(學聯？ 邊撚度聯呀？睇過？）<br />\n<br />\n咁少事都專制到咁<br />\n<br />\n睇撚死你2019 又要未選先告急<br />\n<br />\n早兩個月就屌票又話上次你班焦土撚點點點<br />\n<br />\n張張票都刻撚左泛民個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T03:05:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/110441_c2329af5d8eee5ab1c6a19c06f25294f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F110441_c2329af5d8eee5ab1c6a19c06f25294f.png&h=c8d13938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有圖有證據 泛民支持者見到未？"}]}